Package: realestate-crm
Version: 3.0.0
Section: office
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Essential: no
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pip, python3-venv, sqlite3, adduser
Recommends: python3-pyqt6 (>= 6.4) | python3-pyside6 (>= 6.6), xdg-utils
Suggests: openssh-server, wireguard
Installed-Size: 51200
Maintainer: Muhammad Siddique <info@realestatecrm.com>
Homepage: https://realestatecrm.com
License: Proprietary
Description: Real Estate CRM - Professional Property Management System
 A comprehensive Customer Relationship Management system designed
 specifically for real estate agencies and property managers.
 .
 Features:
  * Rent & Sale deal management with pipeline tracking
  * Property listings with availability management
  * Client & broker contact management
  * Financial tracking (income, expenses, profit/loss)
  * Employee management with attendance & payroll
  * SuccessFactors HR module (employee central, recruiting, performance)
  * Workflow engine with approvals & audit trails
  * AI-powered property matching & insights
  * Multi-user web interface with role-based access
  * Backup & restore functionality
  * Data import/export (CSV, Excel)
  * Dashboard with real-time analytics
 .
 The system runs as a web application on the local network.
 Default admin credentials: admin / admin
 .
 Visit http://localhost:6090 after installation.
